Hey, @fabianschuiki! Please review this at your convenience! Thanks in advance!
This PR is about deleting local variables.
For example:
```
int x, y, z;
always_comb begin
  automatic int a;
  a = x + 1;
  y = a;
  a = a + 1;
  z = a;
end
```
To
```
int x, y, z;
y = x + 1;
z = (x + 1) + 1;
```
Anything about code details could be pointed out.
